title: Fox kit playing in the laundry 🦊

body: I put the question poorly. Are these all the russian domesticated foxes, or does a fox kitty just randomly wander into someone's laundry, or how do people take these photos in the first place? Where I live foxes live in the woods and kill one's chickens, they're not exactly cuddly material.
